    "across all four models, which points to the feature set carrying the signal rather than\n",
    "any single architecture choice. False-alarm counts vary more meaningfully between\n",
    "candidates than recall does, which becomes the deciding factor once confidence intervals\n",
    "are checked in Section 6.4."
